text: Cahul may refer to: *Cahul, a city and municipality in southern Moldova *Cahul District, a district in southern Moldova *Cahul County (Moldova), a former county in Moldova *Cahul County (Romania), a county in Romania *Cahul (wine), a wine region in Moldova *Cahul International Airport, an airport in Moldova, near Cahul *, a lake in Moldova and Ukraine *, a river in Moldova and Ukraine == See also == *Kahul (disambiguation)
